To complete the survey shown in the image, I will follow these steps:

1. Fill in the age field with my age (which is not visible in the image).
2. Select the employment status as "Full-time".
3. Set the watch_time to 4 (assuming this represents the number of hours spent daily on Olympics content during the Olympics period, and I watched for 4 hours a day).
4. Select "Somewhat" for the attention_text_mid field.
5. Set the country_satisfaction to 7.
6. Select "Likely" for the future_interest field.
7. Fill in my favorite moment from the Olympics with a description of one memorable Olympic moment for me.
8. Answer the question about comparing employment status with people in my age group, selecting "Very closely".
9. Move to the next page by clicking on the "Next" button.

```json
  {"tool": "fill", "key": "age", "value": "<your_age>"},

  {"tool": "select", "key": "q_follow_by_age", "value": "Very closely"}
]
```

Please replace `<your_age>` and `<your_favorite_moment>` with the actual values for your age and favorite Olympic moment.
